name: WateredThePlants

skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: watered the plants
des: Living with multiple roommates, or with family and have problems tracking when was the last time someone watered the house plants? Don't over-water or let them dry-out anymore! Just install this skill that helps you keep track of the watering of your plants.
